      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Report: Most 2016 data breaches happened in US&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;GRAND RAPIDS, Mich. (WOOD)  Nearly half of all data breaches in the world in 2016 happened in the U.S., a new report says. The annual report &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://woodtv.com/2017/01/26/report-most-2016-data-breaches-happened-in-us/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://woodtv.com/2017/01/26/report-most-2016-data-breaches-happened-in-us/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Carnegie Mellon privacy clinic aims to help protect you from hackers&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yahoo announced last year the data of about 1.5 billion accounts was compromised in two separate data breaches. And the Allegheny County District &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://triblive.com/local/allegheny/11850094-74/data-privacy-emails&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://triblive.com/local/allegheny/11850094-74/data-privacy-emails&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Without Data Security and Privacy Laws, Medical Records in India Are Highly&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Wire Globally, the medical industry is extremely susceptible to data breaches. The Office of Civil Rights under the US Department of Health and Human &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://thewire.in/102349/without-data-security-and-privacy-laws-medical-records-in-india-are-highly-vulnerable/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://thewire.in/102349/without-data-security-and-privacy-laws-medical-records-in-india-are-highly-vulnerable/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;This risk will double in 2017&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Beazley said its breach response services unit managed 1,943 data breaches on behalf of clients in 2016, up from 1,247 breaches in 2015.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.insurancebusinessmag.com/uk/news/breaking-news/this-risk-will-double-in-2017-58782.aspx&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.insurancebusinessmag.com/uk/news/breaking-news/this-risk-will-double-in-2017-58782.aspx&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;SentinelOne Secures $70 Million To Meet Growing Demand To Replace&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ISBuzz News SentinelOne&amp;rsquo;s next-generation endpoint protection platform is supported on Windows , MacOS and Linux. Time Inc., is the latest in a string of large &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.informationsecuritybuzz.com/news/sentinelone-secures-70-million-meet-growing-demand-replace-traditional-antivirus/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.informationsecuritybuzz.com/news/sentinelone-secures-70-million-meet-growing-demand-replace-traditional-antivirus/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Veracity expands its scope with acquisition of software provider Icomply&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Icomply&amp;rsquo;s product is a command-and-control software system (sometimes called a PSIM, or physical security information management system).  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.sourcesecurity.com/news/articles/veracity-expands-scope-icomply-acquisition-co-227-ga-co-289-ga-co-1437-ga-co-2173-ga-co-8979-ga-co-3329-ga-sb.22318.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.sourcesecurity.com/news/articles/veracity-expands-scope-icomply-acquisition-co-227-ga-co-289-ga-co-1437-ga-co-2173-ga-co-8979-ga-co-3329-ga-sb.22318.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Distribution of definitions to offline endpoints&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;in distribution of definitions to offline endpoints (clients that are either stand &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://community.sophos.com/products/unified-threat-management/f/endpoint-protection-antivirus-and-device-control/86435/distribution-of-definitions-to-offline-endpoints&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://community.sophos.com/products/unified-threat-management/f/endpoint-protection-antivirus-and-device-control/86435/distribution-of-definitions-to-offline-endpoints&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Tieto says 7 out of 10 Swedes worry about internet security&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nine out of ten people want companies who have been exposed to data breaches to inform them about it within 24 hours, according to a survey that &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.telecompaper.com/news/tieto-says-7-out-of-10-swedes-worry-about-internet-security--1181270&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.telecompaper.com/news/tieto-says-7-out-of-10-swedes-worry-about-internet-security--1181270&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Want to cripple your attackers R&amp;amp;D arm? Look for them on your network&amp;hellip;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The security community has coined the phrase &amp;lsquo;threat hunting&amp;rsquo; to describe this process. Conceptually, threat hunting harkens back to the military, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.scmagazine.com/want-to-cripple-your-attackers-rd-arm-look-for-them-on-your-network/article/632500/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.scmagazine.com/want-to-cripple-your-attackers-rd-arm-look-for-them-on-your-network/article/632500/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Shield the datafor your own protection&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If not, how can you say that you are protecting people&amp;rsquo;s data rights and have awareness of data breaches? Have you got some of this data in a &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.tes.com/news/tes-magazine/tes-magazine/shield-datafor-your-own-protection&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.tes.com/news/tes-magazine/tes-magazine/shield-datafor-your-own-protection&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;LeakedSource taken down following raid by FBI&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The site had gained notoriety for the speed with which it acquired stolen credentials, the volume of credentials it offered, and the subscription-based &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.v3.co.uk/v3-uk/news/3003441/leakedsource-taken-down-following-raid-by-fbi&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.v3.co.uk/v3-uk/news/3003441/leakedsource-taken-down-following-raid-by-fbi&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Survey Reveals 64% Americans are Victims of Cybersecurity Breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The lack of security in cyberspace was thrown into sharp relief over the last couple of years with a slew of data breaches rocking the United States.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.christianpost.com/news/survey-reveals-64-americans-are-victims-of-cybersecurity-breaches-173629/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.christianpost.com/news/survey-reveals-64-americans-are-victims-of-cybersecurity-breaches-173629/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;4419 Data Breaches Exposed Over 4.2 Billion Records in 2016&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A total of 4,149 reported data breaches last year exposed more than 4.2 billion records, according to Risk Based Security&amp;rsquo;s 2016 Data Breach &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.esecurityplanet.com/network-security/4419-data-breaches-exposed-over-4.2-billion-records-in-2016.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.esecurityplanet.com/network-security/4419-data-breaches-exposed-over-4.2-billion-records-in-2016.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Breach Notification Website LeakedSource Allegedly Raided, Shut Down&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;LeakedSource, a website dedicated to informing the public about data breaches, has gone offline and it has been 24 hours now since it is down.  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.hackread.com/data-breach-notification-website-leakedsource-raided/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.hackread.com/data-breach-notification-website-leakedsource-raided/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Hacker Tracker: Yahoo In Hot Water, Selfie Security Risks, US Data Breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PYMNTS.com That could mean a selfie app, an email inbox or even within health care and medical services. Eric Chiu, cofounder and president of HyTrust, joined &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.pymnts.com/news/security-and-risk/2017/hacker-tracker-hytrust-yahoo-selfie-security-risks-us-data-breaches-cybersecurity/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.pymnts.com/news/security-and-risk/2017/hacker-tracker-hytrust-yahoo-selfie-security-risks-us-data-breaches-cybersecurity/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Study: Americans do not trust institutions but fail to prote&amp;hellip;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(Pew Research Center)  Cyberattacks and data breaches are facts of life for government agencies, businesses and individuals alike in today&amp;rsquo;s &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.kttn.com/study-americans-do-not-trust-institutions-but-fail-to-protect-their-own-data/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.kttn.com/study-americans-do-not-trust-institutions-but-fail-to-protect-their-own-data/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Vidsys Working with City of Houston To Provide Security During Super Bowl&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Business Wire (press release) VIENNA, Va.&amp;ndash;(BUSINESS WIRE)&amp;ndash;Vidsys, the leading global software technology manufacturer of Physical Security Information Management (PSIM) &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20170127005142/en/Vidsys-Working-City-Houston-Provide-Security-Super&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20170127005142/en/Vidsys-Working-City-Houston-Provide-Security-Super&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;5 Healthcare Facts to Know for Data Privacy Day&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;More Americans trust the healthcare industry with their data than trust the government. But with a sharp rise in healthcare data breaches in 2016, there &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.ajmc.com/newsroom/5-healthcare-facts-to-know-for-data-privacy-day&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.ajmc.com/newsroom/5-healthcare-facts-to-know-for-data-privacy-day&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;2016 was marked by the highest number of data breaches in history&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;the National Law Review and findings by the Identity Theft Resource &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.schooleymitchell.com/blog/2016-marked-highest-number-data-breaches-history&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.schooleymitchell.com/blog/2016-marked-highest-number-data-breaches-history&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Federal Authorities Raid Website That Notifies Of Data Breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;LeakedSource, a well-known website that notifies of data breaches, is unavailable due to being the subject of a federal raid, says a message posted &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.socpedia.com/federal-authorities-raid-website-that-notifies-of-data-breaches&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.socpedia.com/federal-authorities-raid-website-that-notifies-of-data-breaches&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Businesses look to avoid the breach&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PKWARE CEO V. Miller Newton spoke about the dangers of data breaches and his company&amp;rsquo;s work in data encryption Thursday, Jan. 26, at a &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.myozaukeenow.com/story/news/local/2017/01/27/industry-experts-educate-ozaukee-businesses-cyber-security/97145070/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.myozaukeenow.com/story/news/local/2017/01/27/industry-experts-educate-ozaukee-businesses-cyber-security/97145070/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;FCC Report Pushes for Stronger Data Breach Reporting Requirements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Customers might not realize when data breaches occur that don&amp;rsquo;t affect the ability of Internet service providers to continue functioning normally; &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.meritalk.com/articles/fcc-report-pushes-for-stronger-data-breach-reporting-requirements/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.meritalk.com/articles/fcc-report-pushes-for-stronger-data-breach-reporting-requirements/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;LeakedSource&amp;rsquo;s shutdown is a blow to amateur hackers&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I see a lot of data breaches in my travels but I was still shocked to see my own personal information sold in this way, he wrote. My birth date.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.itworld.com/article/3162496/security/leakedsources-shutdown-is-a-blow-to-amateur-hackers.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.itworld.com/article/3162496/security/leakedsources-shutdown-is-a-blow-to-amateur-hackers.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Scope of medical data breaches unknown in Delaware&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A Protenus study found that the number of data breaches nearly doubled from 2015 to 2016, averaging more than one data breach per day.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.delawareonline.com/story/news/2017/01/27/scope-medical-data-breaches-unknown-delaware/96493240/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.delawareonline.com/story/news/2017/01/27/scope-medical-data-breaches-unknown-delaware/96493240/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
